{
  "stem": "9415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got out of the wagon, and we were separated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what happened to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were only one day in this camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then, next day, we went another train and took us to Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took us to Germany next day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The place-- the first place was Hessental.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's near Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything's near south Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember we worked there with-- cutting stones or something, that's all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there for a couple of weeks, and then they took us to Vaihingen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vaihingen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "V-A-H-I-H-I-N-G-E-N, Vaihingen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a working camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went every day to work in the morning, all kind of jobs, especially they brought-- the last time, we worked in the underground factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were building a underground factory because, you know, the airplanes used to come over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "British airplanes came over all the time and bombarded the-- all around this place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to end this, we were working in the factory at night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a night shift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "During the night, British airplanes came in and bombarded the hole where the factory was supposed to be built, but the Germans run out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took place in special-- the places safe-- for safety.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were to stand out in the-- in the hole and watch that airplanes coming and bombarding the place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was the worst place in camp, where-- this place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then, we were transported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took us out from this camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was when the American army start coming into Germany-- into Germany from the west.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we were transported to Dachau, Allach, Dachau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dachau is near Munich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's about 20 miles, I think, from Munich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Dachau, we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was-- Dachau was Allach, Dachau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
